---
title: Music
description: Music is one of my passions. Check out all my musical projects here.
layout: primary
pageName: musicPage
addCSS: true
addJS: true
plvylist: true
---
{%- set logoWidths = [300, 600] -%}
{%- set logoFormats = ['webp', 'png'] -%}
{%- set logoSizes = '(max-width: 700px) 96vw, 300px' -%}
<main class="layout">
  <header class="page-header center">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1><span id="music-title">{{ title }}</span></h1>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="bands-container">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="content center">
        <section class="section-header">
          <h2>Here Are My Bands</h2>
          <p>I write for a few projects, so here they are with all the important links. Music is best managed elsewhere than my personal website, so you're better off visiting those places.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="bands">
          <div class="band">
            <div class="band-logo">
              <a href="https://frontroyalmd.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                {% image './src/assets/img/front-royal-logo-white_400x240.png', 'the logo for my band, Front Royal', logoWidths, logoFormats, logoSizes, 'full' %}
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="icon-bar">
              {%- for social in music.frontRoyalSocial -%}
                <a class="icon-link" href="{{ social.href }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/assets/img/{{ social.img }}" alt="{{ social.alt }}" loading="lazy" width="48" height="48"></a>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="band">
            <div class="band-logo">
              <a href="https://justtroy.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                {% image './src/assets/img/troy-full.png', 'the logo for my band, troy', logoWidths, logoFormats, logoSizes, 'full' %}
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="icon-bar">
              {%- for social in music.troySocial -%}
                <a class="icon-link" href="{{ social.href }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/assets/img/{{ social.img }}" alt="{{ social.alt }}" loading="lazy" width="48" height="48"></a>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="music-player">
    <div class="wrapper" data-constrain="more">
      <header class="center">
        <h2>Stream <span class="italic" id="album-title">Alone In A Crowded Room</span></h2>
        <p>I created my own embedded streaming player, called <span class="italic">Plvylist</span>, because I wanted to understand how web audio works. Check it out in action.</p>
      </header>
      <plvylist-player
              audio-location="/assets/audio/"
              artist-name="troy."
              album-name="Alone In A Crowded Room"
              cover-art="/assets/img/aiacr.jpg"
              placeholder-image="/assets/img/missingart.png">
      </plvylist-player>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
